title: FBI has 'grave concerns' over GOP memo's accuracy
text:
FBI has 'grave concerns' over GOP memo's accuracy Wednesday, January 31, 2018 - 02:01 
The FBI publicly came out against the release of a contentious classified memo written by Republicans alleging the FBI abused its surveillance power. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
